Name:           Google Hot Trends Atom Scraper
URL:            http://www.fromzerotoseo.com/coding/
Last updated:   May 14, 2009
License:        No license needed

Installation:

1. Import database "sql/trends.sql".
2. Configure parameters "share/config.php":
    1) Database address DB_ADDR, default "localhost".
    2) Login DB_USER, default "root".
    3) Password DB_PSWD, default "".
    4) Database name DB_NAME, default "trends".
3. Set up an hourly cron job "cron/cron.php".
